BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:20260403-1226863@ukmovies
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260403
SUMMARY:The Super Mario Galaxy Movie
DESCRIPTION:Runtime: 98 minutes\nRating: 0.0\nGenres: Family\, Fantasy\, Comedy\, Adventure\, Animation\n\nHaving thwarted Bowser's previous plot to marry Princess Peach\, Mario and Luigi now face a fresh threat in Bowser Jr.\, who is determined to liberate his father from captivity and restore the family legacy. Alongside companions new and old\, the brothers travel across the stars to stop the young heir's crusade.\n\nTrailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=En5QZmL5R1s
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:20260506-1301421@ukmovies
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260506
SUMMARY:The Sheep Detectives
DESCRIPTION:Runtime: 0 minutes\nRating: 0.0\nGenres: Mystery\, Crime\, Comedy\, Family\n\nGeorge is a shepherd who reads detective novels to his beloved sheep every night\, assuming they can't possibly understand. But when a mysterious incident disrupts life on the farm\, the sheep realize they must become the detectives. As they follow the clues and investigate human suspects\, they prove that even sheep can be brilliant crime-solvers.\n\nTrailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pyZI5oM6hWk
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:20260514-1122573@ukmovies
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260514
SUMMARY:In the Grey
DESCRIPTION:Runtime: 0 minutes\nRating: 0.0\nGenres: Action\, Thriller\n\nWhen a ruthless despot steals a billion-dollar fortune\, a covert team of elite operatives who live in the global shadows\, as comfortable wielding power and influence as they are automatic weapons and high explosives\, is sent to steal it back on what would be for anyone else a suicide mission. What begins as an impossible heist gets much worse\, spiraling into an all-out war of strategy\, deception and survival.\n\nTrailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nufP15iN4GE
END:VEVENT

